        <b>March 2025 </b> - I presented a poster detailing my work on time-reversal symmetry breaking in vision (the aformentioned paper) at <a href="https://www.cosyne.org/" target="_blank">COSYNE</a> 2025 in Montreal.
    </p>

    <p>
        <b>March 2025 </b> - My very first <a href="https://www.pnas.org/doi/10.1073/pnas.2410768122" target = "_blank">paper</a>, titled "Broken time-reversal symmetry in visual motion detection," was published in PNAS (featuring some photos of me hiking in Yosemite)! 
